### M-Pesa Integration Test Collection

## SETUP
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api
@authToken = {{YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN}}
@companId = {{YOUR_COMPANY_ID}}

---

## 1. STK PUSH - Initiate Payment
POST {{baseUrl}}/mpesa/stk-push
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone_number": "25470837149",
  "amount": 100,
  "account_reference": "REF" + @ts,
  "transaction_desc": "Test Payment"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("checkoutRequestId", response.body.transaction.checkout_request_id);
  client.global.set("transactionId", response.body.transaction.id);
  client.log("Checkout Request ID: " + response.body.transaction.checkout_request_id);
  client.log("Transaction ID: " + response.body.transaction.id);
%}

---

## 2. STATUS QUERY - Check Payment Status (Before User Response)
POST {{baseUrl}}/mpesa/stk-query
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "checkout_request_id": "{{checkoutRequestId}}"
}

> {%
  client.log("Transaction Status: " + response.body.transaction.status);
  client.log("Result Code: " + response.body.transaction.result_code);
  client.log("Result Desc: " + response.body.transaction.result_desc);
%}

---

## 3. SIMULATE CALLBACK - User Accepts Payment
POST {{baseUrl}}/mpesa/test-callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "checkout_request_id": "{{checkoutRequestId}}",
  "result_code": "0",
  "result_desc": "The service request is processed successfully.",
  "receipt_number": "TEG8M0IY4U"
}

> {%
  client.log("Test Callback Response: " + JSON.stringify(response.body));
%}

---

## 4. STATUS QUERY - Check Payment Status (After User Accepts)
POST {{baseUrl}}/mpesa/stk-query
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "checkout_request_id": "{{checkoutRequestId}}"
}

> {%
  client.log("Final Status: " + response.body.transaction.status);
  client.log("Receipt Number: " + response.body.transaction.mpesa_receipt_number);
%}

---

## 5. GET TRANSACTION - Retrieve Transaction Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/mpesa/transactions/{{checkoutRequestId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

---

## ALTERNATIVE: SIMULATE USER CANCELS PAYMENT

POST {{baseUrl}}/mpesa/test-callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "checkout_request_id": "{{checkoutRequestId}}",
  "result_code": "1032",
  "result_desc": "Request canceled by the user"
}

---

## NOTES:

1. **Get Auth Token:**
   - POST /api/login with your credentials
   - Copy the token from response

2. **Test Credentials (Safaricom Sandbox):**
   - Phone: 25470837149
   - Amount: Any amount (will be simulated)
   - Shortcode: 174379
   - Passkey: bfb279f9aa9bdbcf158e97dd71a467cd2e0c893059b10f78e6b72ada1ed2c919

3. **Result Codes:**
   - 0: Success
   - 1032: User cancelled
   - Other codes: Various failures

4. **Testing Flow:**
   - Step 1: Initiate STK push (prompts user)
   - Step 2: Query status before user responds (should be pending)
   - Step 3: Simulate callback (simulates user accepting/declining)
   - Step 4: Query status after callback (should reflect user action)
   - Step 5: Get full transaction details

5. **Production vs Development:**
   - Test callback endpoint (Step 3) only available in development
   - In production, actual M-Pesa callbacks will trigger the /mpesa/callback endpoint
